data.description: This property presents an opportunity to own a stunning home in a highly desirable location.With impressive features and convenient amenities, this property will exceed your expectations.As you step inside, you'll discover a thoughtfully designed layout, with all bedrooms situated upstairs, ensuring privacy and separation from the living areas.The loft, which is ideal for a study area or play area for the children, adds versatility and flexibility to the property.With a fenced yard and no homes located behind it, this property offers additional privacy and tranquility, as it backs up to an equestrian farm.Additionally, the screened patio/lanai, provides a delightful space for relaxation and outdoor enjoyment.Whether you're savoring a morning cup of coffee or hosting a barbecue this area offers a comfortable retreat.The kitchen is a true chef's dream, equipped with Whirlpool stainless steel appliances, including a gas stove and granite counters this kitchen offers both elegance and functionality.Take a refreshing swim in the community pool, relax in the hot tub, or socialize at the clubhouse or fitness center.
